How It Works

Our blockchain identity system is designed to be simple, secure, and user-friendly. Here's how you can get started:

  1. 1Register your identity by providing your document ID and a profile picture.
  2. 2Your information is securely encrypted and stored on the blockchain.
  3. 3Authorized users can verify your identity without accessing your personal data.
  4. 4You maintain full control over your identity and can revoke access at any time.
